dcterms:description: A dataset generated from the Lotka-Volterra equations, which model the dynamics of predator and prey populations using nonlinear differential equations.

dcterms:description: A dataset based on the Lorenz attractor, a three-dimensional nonlinear dynamical system originally developed to model atmospheric convection.
